fr.apteryx.imageio.dicom
Class StorageCommitmentInformation

Object
  StorageCommitmentInformation
Direct Known Subclasses:
StorageCommitmentSCP.Request, StorageCommitmentSCU.Request, StorageCommitmentSCU.Result
public abstract class StorageCommitmentInformation
extends Object

Instances of this class are used either SCU-side or SCP-side of the Storage Commitment Service Class to either specify the SOP instances which safekeeping is requested or the result of such request.

getTransactionUID

public String getTransactionUID()
Returns the transaction UID that is needed to match requests sent by an SCU with the results received. When using an evaluation version, transaction uid created by the plugin are always return "0.0.0.0.0".
